Disclaimer: Active development in process. Some features/settings may not work properly.

Instagram Bot for following users based on csv file and comments on pictures.

Uses OCR to capture data on the screen, Pyautogui to mimic realistic movement, and Tesseract to capture screenshots and use AI to determine what to comment.


Dependencies:
Download Python: https://www.python.org/downloads/
Download Git: https://git-scm.com/downloads
Download Tesseract: https://github.com/UB-Mannheim/tesseract/wiki


Create python environment: python -m venv env
Activate environment: env\Scripts\activate
Install requirements: python -m pip install -r requirements.txt


Run program: 
cd InstaPyBot
env\Scripts\activate
python main.py
